Global Torpedo Launcher Market Insights
Torpedo Launcher Market size was valued at USD 3.12 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 4.85 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 5.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Torpedo Launcher Market Overview
The global torpedo launcher market is projected to experience significant growth in the coming years. With increasing defense budgets and advancements in naval warfare technologies, the market is expected to reach a market value of USD 2.5 billion by 2030, growing at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of approximately 5.1% from 2023 to 2030. The growth is driven by the rising demand for enhanced defense capabilities, along with the increasing integration of modern technology in military systems. The development of smart and autonomous torpedoes is also contributing to the growing adoption of torpedo launchers in naval fleets.

